All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AlarmController
    The Class AlarmController, implements both IAlarmListener and IStockListener.
    AlarmUnit
    The Class AlarmUnit contains all information about a chart alarm packaged into one object: the stock information, the threshold, the alarm position and its drawing color.
    AlarmView
    The Class AlarmView offers a single method to show a dialog when a stock alarm is fired because a threshold has been crossed.
    BaseInternalFrame
    The Class BaseInternalFrame provides all shared settings for the internal frame sub classes used in the Stocker application.
    BollingerBand
    The Class BollingerBand contains all information of a Bollinger Band indicator object: the values of the Bollinger Bands, the Simple Moving Average and the parameters used to calculate them.
    ChartCandle
    The Class ChartCandle is a wrapper class containing all data for a candle object.
    ChartFrame
    The Class ChartFrame provides the frame for all chart related drawings, while the drawing itself takes place in the ChartPanel class.
    ChartPanel
    The Class ChartPanel is responsible for drawing the stock information and chart indicators.
    ControllerTest  
    DataPersistenceModel
    The Class DataPersistenceModel is a wrapper class for all data needed to save the current state of the data base model to disk and restore it from there.
    DataProvider
    The Class DataProvider containing all relevant information for the network interface to connect to the data provider.
    DataProvTableModel
    The Class DataProvTableModel extends AbstractTableModel to display information about the available data providers in the preferences dialog.
    EAlarmPos
    The Enum EAlarmPos is used to store if the alarm was when the current stock price is above or below the threshold.
    EChartResolution
    The Enum EChartResolution used for data fetching and displaying the correct data for the requested interval.
    EChartType
    The Enum EChartType to set which type of chart gets painted.
    EFrameType
    The Enum EFrameType to store the type of internal frames.
    EnterApiKeyDialog
    The sole purpose of the Class EnterApiKeyDialog is to show a dialog prompting the user to enter a missing API key for one of the data providers.
    EPullOperation
    The Enum EPullOperation enumerates all possible API requests/HTTP pull operations and their corresponding URL paths.
    FramePersistenceModel
    The Class FramePersistenceModel is a wrapper class for all data needed to save the current state of the GUI to disk and restore it from there.
    IAlarmListener
    The listener interface for the method being called when a new alarm is added in the model.
    IMainController
    The Interface IMainController is implemented by the main controller of the stocker program and allows the separate functional units to communicate with each other according to the mediator pattern.
    INetworkController
    The Interface INetworkController implemented by the network controller to handle data providers and API requests.
    IPreferencesController
    The Interface IPreferencesController offers the abstract methods to handle preference changes and to get information from the preference controller.
    IPushSubscriber
    The Interface IPushSubscriber implemented by the class handling the incoming push messages from the network.
    IStockerModel
    The Interface IStockerModel details all public data base methods.
    IStockItem
    The Interface IStockItem is implemented by the stock item objects in the data base model and offers the methods to access all relevant data of the stock.
    IStockListener
    The listener interface for receiving notifications when the price and data of a stock has been updated.
    JsonFactory
    A factory for creating Java objects from JSON strings and creating JSON strings from Java objects.
    JsonHistCandle
    The Class JsonHistCandle contains the arrays of historical candle data received from the data provider.
    JsonQuoteObject
    The Class JsonQuoteObject contains the information received from the data provider as a response to a quote request.
    JsonSearchObject
    The Class JsonSearchObject is a wrapper class for the response to a search request delivered by the data provider.
    JsonSearchResult
    The Class JsonSearchResult contains the information of a single search result delivered by the data provider.
    JsonTradeObject
    The Class JsonTradeObject is a wrapper class for new push data delivered by the data provider.
    MainController
    The Class MainController implements the interface IMainController to allow the separate functional units to communicate with each other according to the mediator pattern.
    MainFrame
    The Class MainFrame extends a JFrame, whose main part is a desktop pane for all the internal frame from the different parts of the application.
    NetworkController
    The Class NetworkController implements the INetworkInterface and handles the connections to the data provider.
    OpenFrame
    The Class OpenFrame is used for collecting information about all open internal frames displayed in the application main frame.
    PaintableChartComponent
    The Class PaintableChartComponent is an abstract super class of all classes whose objects can also be painted on a chart frame.
    PersistenceController
    The Class PersistenceController is responsible for writing the persistence models to disk and for restoring the application state from the models when they are read from file.
    PersistenceModelWrapper
    The Class PersistenceModelWrapper is a wrapper class gathering all three parts of the application persistence into one model.
    PreferencesController
    The PreferencesController handles the coordination between the user preferences and the different parts of the application so that every part knows the preferences that are relevant for it.
    PreferencesFrame
    The Class PreferencesFrame displays the preferences dialog allowing the user to change the change application settings.
    PreferencesModel
    The Class PreferencesModel contains all currently active preference settings and their corresponding defaults.
    PushClient
    The Class PushClient used to connect to the web socket server of a data provider, sending and receiving messages.
    SearchFrame
    The Class SearchFrame shows the search frame, allows the user to search and to interact with the results.
    SearchResult
    The Class SearchResult is a wrapper class containing all information for a single search result parsed from a data provider response.
    SearchResultTableModel
    The Class SearchResultTableModel extends AbstractTableModel to display information about the results of a search request specifically in the format to display them in a search frame.
    SimpleMovingAverage
    The Class SimpleMovingAverage contains all information of a Simple Moving Average indicator object: the values of the Simple Moving Average and the parameter used to calculate it.
    StockCalcHelper
    The Class StockCalcHelper is a calculator class with static methods to perform operations on inputs of values.
    Stocker_3266494_Rudolph_Matthias  
    StockerModel
    The Class StockerModel is the central data base model for the Stocker application.
    StockerTest_3266494_Rudolph_Matthias  
    StockerTesterImpl  
    StockItem
    The Class StockItem is part of the data model, storing all stock-related data for a specific stock.
    TradeDataUnit
    The Class TradeDataUnit is a data wrapper class used to process the updated stock information coming in through a push update from the data provider.
    WatchlistFrame
    The Class WatchlistFrame shows the watchlist and allows the user to interact with its content.
    WatchlistTableModel
    The Class WatchlistTableModel extends AbstractTableModel to display the contents of the watchlist specifically in the format to display them in a watchlist frame.
